dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until order items received (days)",
    "Time until FI-AP items creation (days)",
    "Time until FI-AP items cleared (days)",
    "Over-Deliveries (%)",
    "GR receipt created late (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Stock transport order items received")
        	AS "Time until order items received (days)",
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - FI-AR items created") 
        	AS "Time until FI-AP items creation (days)",
		AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - FI-AP items cleared") 
        	AS "Time until FI-AP items cleared (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Stock transport order items with overdelivery") * 100 
        	AS "Over-Deliveries (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Stock transport order items with goods receipt created later than planned") * 100 
        	AS "GR receipt created late (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
